(7438, 1, '2013-03-09 00:29:36', '2013-03-09 00:29:36', '[impact_text include_button="yes" button_style="standard" title="Buy now" href="/features/" color="accent" size="normal" type="roundedarrow" target="_self" position="cta_align_right" alt_background="alt-seven" el_class="mb0 mt0 bt0" width="1/1" el_position="first last"]\n<h2>Neighborhood: A clean, responsive &amp; retina-ready multipurpose eCommerce WordPress theme.</h2>\n[/impact_text] [blank_spacer height="60px" width="1/1" el_position="first last"] [spb_text_block title="Incredibly Responsive" icon="fa-mobile-phone" pb_margin_bottom="no" pb_border_bottom="no" width="1/4" el_position="first"]\n\nNeighborhood is completely responsive. And when we say responsive, we mean it wont only work on mobile devices; itll look damn good!\n\n<a class="read-more" href="/features#responsive">Find out more <i class="icon-chevron-right">&gt;</i></a>\n\n[/spb_text_block] [spb_text_block title="Swift Page Builder" icon="fa-pencil" pb_margin_bottom="no" pb_border_bottom="no" width="1/4"]\n\nQuickly &amp; easily create beautiful pages. Choose any combination of 40 elements to create unique pages that do your content justice.\n\n<a class="read-more" href="/features#pagebuilder">Find out more <i class="icon-chevron-right">&gt;</i></a>\n\n[/spb_text_block] [spb_text_block title="Superior Typography" icon="fa-font" pb_margin_bottom="no" pb_border_bottom="no" width="1/4"]\n\nNeighborhood includes pro Font Deck support. Or you can choose from 600+ Google Web fonts &amp; control the colour, size &amp; line height.\n\n<a class="read-more" href="/features#fonts">Find out more <i class="icon-chevron-right">&gt;</i></a>\n\n[/spb_text_block] [spb_text_block title="Stunning Sliders" icon="fa-eye" pb_margin_bottom="no" pb_border_bottom="no" width="1/4" el_position="last"]\n\nNeighborhood comes with 2 sliders included. The ever popular Revolution Slider and our own innovative and stunning Swift Slider.\n\n<a class="read-more" href="/features#s