(10282, 1, '2013-07-12 13:12:27', '2013-07-12 13:12:27', '[fullwidth_text alt_background="alt-seven" el_class="mt0 mb0 pb0 pmb0 bt0 bb0 no-arrow" width="1/1" el_position="first last"]\n<h1 style="text-align: center;">Update V2.17 - 22ndApril 2015</h1>\n<ul>\n	<li>Updated implemented plugins with security fixes</li>\n	<li>Added Support for WooCommerce 2.3.8</li>\n	<li>Added captions to product image lightbox</li>\n	<li>Fixed issue with variation change and lightbox</li>\n	<li>Fixed issue with vimeo thumbnail loading in Flash format</li>\n</ul>\n[/fullwidth_text] [fullwidth_text alt_background="alt-seven" el_class="mt0 mb0 pb0 pmb0 bt0 bb0 no-arrow" width="1/1" el_position="first last"]\n<h1 style="text-align: center;">Update V2.16 - 16th March2015</h1>\n<ul>\n	<li>Added WooCommerce 2.3.6 support</li>\n	<li>Added custom quantity controls to products</li>\n	<li>Fixed issues with Wishlist since plugin update</li>\n	<li>Fixed incompatibility with WooCommerce Quickview plugin</li>\n</ul>\n[/fullwidth_text] [fullwidth_text alt_background="alt-seven" el_class="mt0 mb0 pb0 pmb0 bt0 bb0 no-arrow" width="1/1" el_position="first last"]\n<h1 style="text-align: center;">Update V2.12 - 13th February2015</h1>\n<ul>\n	<li>Fixed issue with payment descriptions on checkout</li>\n	<li>Fixed issue with cart showing two shipping calculators</li>\n</ul>\n[/fullwidth_text] [blank_spacer height="30px" width="1/1" el_position="first last"] [fullwidth_text alt_background="alt-seven" el_class="mt0 mb0 pb0 pmb0 bt0 bb0 no-arrow" width="1/1" el_position="first last"]\n<h1 style="text-align: center;">Update V2.11 - 12th February2015</h1>\n<ul>\n	<li>Updated to support WooCommerce 2.3.3</li>\n	<li>Updated Isotope script</li>\n	<li>Fixed header cart to include tax when enabled</li>\n	<li>Fixed styling issue with variable product add to cart button</li>\n	<li>Fixed Quickview styling</li>\n	<li>Fixed missing translation strings</li>\n</ul>\n[/fullwidth_text] [blank_spacer height="30px" width="1/1" el_position="first last"] [fullwidth_text alt_background="alt-seven" el_class="mt0 mb0 pb0 pmb0 bt0 bb0 no-arrow" width="1/1" el_position="first last"]\n<h1 style="text-align: center;">Update V2.10 - 30th January2015</h1>\n<ul>\n	<li>Added support for WooCommerce 2.3.</li>\n	<li>Added Lato to Google Font options.</li>\n	<li>Added option to show product short description on shop pages.</li>\n	<li>Updated to Font Awesome 4.3.</li>\n	<li>Fixed issue with image asset caption output.</li>\n	<li>Fixed issue with icon shortcode.</li>\n	<li>Fixed issue with super search showing draft prices.</li>\n</ul>\n[/fullwidth_text] [blank_spacer height="30px" width="1/1" el_position="first last"] [fullwidth_text alt_background="alt-seven" el_class="mt0 mb0 pb0 pmb0 bt0 bb0 no-arrow" width="1/1" el_position="first last"]\n<h1 style="text-align: center;">Update V2.05 - 22ndDecember2014</h1>\n<ul>\n	<li>Improved header wishlist dropdown to update via AJAX</li>\n	<li>Fixed issue with missing product image when WPML active</li>\n	<li>Fixed translation issues</li>\n	<li>Fixed products layout issue on mobile devices</li>\n	<li>Fixed other minor issues</li>\n</ul>\n[/fullwidth_text] [blank_spacer height="30px" width="1/1" el_position="first last"] [fullwidth_text alt_background="alt-seven" el_class="mt0 mb0 pb0 pmb0 bt0 bb0 no-arrow" width="1/1" el_position="first last"]\n<h1 style="text-align: center;">Update V2.03 - 4th December2014</h1>\n<ul>\n	<li>Minor page builder improvements.</li>\n	<li>Adjusted page builder shortcode loading.</li>\n	<li>Fixed issue with logo size on mobile.</li>\n	<li>Minor styling fixes.</li>\n</ul>\n[/fullwidth_text] [blank_spacer height="30px" width="1/1" el_position="first last"] [fullwidth_text alt_background="alt-seven" el_class="mt0 mb0 pb0 pmb0 bt0 bb0 no-arrow" width="1/1" el_position="first last"]\n<h1 style="text-align: center;">Update V2.02 - 28th November2014</h1>\n<ul>\n	<li>Added lightbox options to theme options - arrows/thumbs/skin/sharing</li>\n	<li>Fixed JS error on 2.01</li>\n</ul>\n[/fullwidth_text] [blank_spacer height="30px" width="1/1" el_position="first last"] [fullwidth_text alt_background="alt-seven" el_class="mt0 mb0 pb0 pmb0 bt0 bb0 no-arrow" width="1/1" el_position="first last"]\n<h1 style="text-align: center;">Update V2.01 - 28th November2014</h1>\n<ul>\n	<li>Added logo height &amp; padding options, for greater control</li>\n	<li>Fixed issue with mobile menu sub-menu width</li>\n	<li>Fixed issue with carousels not displaying</li>\n	<li>Fixed issue with product share(s) not including title</li>\n	<li>Fixed issue with lightbox not being navigateable for a gallery</li>\n</ul>\n[button colour="black" type="slightlyroundedarrow" size="medium" link="http://neighborhood.swiftideas.net/img/neighborhood_changelog_2.01.png" target="_blank"]2.01 Changelog[/button]\n\n[/fullwidth_text] [blank_spacer height="30px" width="1/1" el_position="first last"] [fullwidth_text alt_background="alt-seven" el_class="mt0 mb0 pb0 pmb0 bt0 bb0 no-arrow" width="1/1" el_position="first last"]\n<h1 style="text-align: center;">Update V2 - 26th November2014</h1>\n[hr] [one_half] [list type="add"] [list_item]Added Mega Menu Functionality - You can now enable mega menu on a per menu item basis, and select how many mega menu columns are shown[/list_item] [list_item]Added iLightbox lightbox script - Super slick lightbox functionality, across all aspects of the theme including product images. Set the lightbox skin, thumbnails, sharing, and arrow options[/list_item] [list_item]Added custom post type permalink rewrite options- You can now define custom URL rewrite for portfolio/team[/list_item] [list_item]Added option of outputting product categories from the Product page builder asset[/list_item] [list_item]Added option to set header search to only show product results[/list_item] [list_item]Added Super Search Page Builder asset- You can now add the super search asset anywhere within your page builder pages[/list_item][list_item]Added Social Share shortcode to the shortcode generator[/list_item] [/list] [/one_half] [one_half_last] [list type="tick_bw"] [list_item]Improved product zoom- You can now use touch to zoom the product images on your mobile devices[/list_item] [list_item]Improved header logo / menu height adjustment based on logo size, now set automatically based on the logo image size[/list_item] [list_item]Improved Page Builder edit modal sizing[/list_item] [list_item]Updated Masonry script for better performance[/list_item] [list_item]Fixed various issues[/list_item] [/list] [/one_half_last]\n\n[button colour="black" type="slightlyroundedarrow" size="medium" link="http://neighborhood.swiftideas.net/img/neighborhood_changelog_2.0.png" target="_blank"]2.0 Changelog[/button]\n\n[/fullwidth_text] [blank_spacer height="30px" width="1/1" el_position="first last"] [fullwidth_text alt_background="alt-seven" el_class="mt0 mb0 pb0 pmb0 bt0 bb0 no-arrow" width="1/1" el_position="first last"]\n<h1 style="text-align: center;">Update V1.9 - 1stSeptember 2014</h1>\n[hr]\n\n&nbsp;\n\n[/fullwidth_text] [spb_text_block pb_margin_bottom="no" pb_border_bottom="no" width="1/1" el_position="first last"]\n\n&nbsp;\n\n[list type="add"] [list_item]Added Image Banner shortcode[/list_item] [list_item]Majorly improved product image loading[/list_item] [/list] [list type="tick_bw"] [list_item]Fixed issue with product category navigation not showing[/list_item] [list_item]Fixed issue with product carousel on portfolio items[/list_item] [list_item]Fixed issue with page builder text formatting[/list_item] [/list]\n\n&nbsp;\n\n[/spb_text_block] [fullwidth_text alt_background="alt-seven" el_class="mt0 mb0 pb0 pmb0 bt0 bb0 no-arrow" width="1/1" el_position="first last"]\n\n&nbsp;\n<h1 style="text-align: center;">Update V1.8 - 17th June2014</h1>\n[hr] [one_half] [list type="add"] [list_item]Major performance improvements, drastically reducing database queries[/list_item] [list_item]Added search functionality to header 4 &amp; 5 options[/list_item] [list_item]Added holding page template, with no header/footer[/list_item] [/list] [/one_half] [one_half_last] [list type="tick_bw"] [list_item]Fixed issue with page builder text block not saving in text mode[/list_item] [list_item]Fixed product slider to allow use of navigation arrows with zoom enabled[/list_item] [list_item]Fixed issue with cart dropdown showing incorrect buttons when no items in cart[/list_item] [list_item]Fixed issue with product carousel on mobile[/list_item] [/list] [/one_half_last]\n\n&nbsp;\n\n[/fullwidth_text] [fullwidth_text alt_background="alt-seven" el_class="mt0 mb0 pb0 pmb0 bt0 bb0 no-arrow" width="1/1" el_position="first last"]\n\n&nbsp;\n<h1 style="text-align: center;">Update V1.7 - 17th April 2014</h1>\n[hr] [one_half] [list type="add"] [list_item]Added RTL support[/list_item] [list_item]Added WordPress 3.9 compatibility[/list_item] [list_item]Updated necessary files for WooCommerce 2.1.7 update[/list_item] [list_item]Improved mobile header to show on iPad landscape as well as portrait - for better usability[/list_item] [list_item]Improved product zoom performance and integration, as well as fixing the overlay issues[/list_item] [list_item]Improved product description + short description meta boxes to be wysiwyg editors[/list_item] [/list] [/one_half] [one_half_last] [list type="tick_bw"] [list_item]Fixed issue with product schema[/list_item] [list_item]Fixed issue with menu dropdown going behind image/banners in some circumstances[/list_item] [list_item]Fixed an issue with the page builder single image asset causing a slow down[/list_item] [list_item]Fixed issue with product image height when product asset with mini display type used[/list_item] [list_item]Adjusted styling for product enquiry plugin[/list_item] [/list] [/one_half_last]\n\n&nbsp;\n\n[/fullwidth_text] [fullwidth_text alt_background="alt-seven" el_class="mt0 mb0 pb0 pmb0 bt0 bb0 no-arrow" width="1/1" el_position="first last"]\n\n&nbsp;\n<h1 style="text-align: center;">Update V1.6 - 10th February 2014</h1>\n[hr] [one_half] [list type="add"] [list_item]Added support for WooCommerce 2.1[/list_item][list_item]Added function override checks to sf-woocommerce.php[/list_item] [list_item] Added Google Font subset support in the Font Theme Options panel[/list_item] [/list] [/one_half] [one_half_last] [list type="tick_bw"] [list_item]Fixed issue with google font weight/style[/list_item] [list_item]Fixed issue with cart/wishlist on Header 5[/list_item] [list_item]Fixed issue with cart page, previously did not validate[/list_item] [list_item]Fixed issue with default product meta[/list_item] [list_item]Fixed issue with badges not showing[/list_item] [list_item]Fixed alt 10 text colour[/list_item] [list_item]Fixed issue with layer slider within posts[/list_item] [list_item]Fixed issue with product image gap when add to cart caption is hidden[/list_item] [list_item]Fixed issue with theme options panel not loading correctly[/list_item] [list_item]Fixed issue where search would show on mobile when disabled[/list_item] [/list] [/one_half_last]\n\n&nbsp;\n\n[/fullwidth_text] [fullwidth_text alt_background="alt-seven" el_class="mt0 mb0 pb0 pmb0 bt0 bb0 no-arrow" width="1/1" el_position="first last"]\n\n&nbsp;\n<h1 style="text-align: center;">Update V1.55 - 18th January 2014</h1>\n[hr] [one_half] [list type="add"] [list_item]Improved WordPress 3.8 styling, new custom post type icons[/list_item] [/list] [/one_half] [one_half_last] [list type="tick_bw"] [list_item]Fixed WooCommerce badges not showing on fade transition[/list_item] [list_item]Fixed issue with image banner content on tablet/mobile[/list_item] [list_item]Fixed ajax-loader.gif URL[/list_item] [list_item]Fixed issue with products sale display ignoring the category[/list_item] [/list] [/one_half_last]\n\n&nbsp;\n\n[/fullwidth_text] [fullwidth_text alt_background="alt-seven" el_class="mt0 mb0 pb0 pmb0 bt0 bb0 no-arrow" width="1/1" el_position="first last"]\n\n&nbsp;\n<h1 style="text-align: center;">Update V1.53 - 10th January 2014</h1>\n[hr] [one_half] [list type="add"] [list_item]Added new revolution slider version export[/list_item] [list_item]Added spanish translation, thanks to miguelsoler[/list_item] [list_item]Added option to disable the header search[/list_item] [list_item]Added Xing social icon option[/list_item] [list_item]Improved checkout page split[/list_item] [list_item]Improved WooCommerce active check[/list_item] [list_item]Improved welcome message header to only show when WooCommerce enabled[/list_item] [/list] [/one_half] [one_half_last] [list type="tick_bw"] [list_item]Fixed standard category display issue[/list_item] [list_item]Fixed issue with carousels, that would cause resize loop[/list_item] [list_item]Fixed chart scale showing in IE8[/list_item] [/list] [/one_half_last]\n\n&nbsp;\n\n[/fullwidth_text] [fullwidth_text alt_background="alt-seven" el_class="mt0 mb0 pb0 pmb0 bt0 bb0 no-arrow" width="1/1" el_position="first last"]\n\n&nbsp;\n<h1 style="text-align: center;">Update V1.52 - 18th December 2013</h1>\n[hr] [list type="tick_bw"] [list_item]Fixed issue with Twitter oAuth[/list_item] [list_item]Fixed issue with image banner shortcode generator[/list_item] [list_item]Fixed issue with product thumbnail showing twice on product page[/list_item] [/list]\n\n&nbsp;\n\n[/fullwidth_text] [fullwidth_text alt_background="alt-seven" el_class="mt0 mb0 pb0 pmb0 bt0 bb0 no-arrow" width="1/1" el_position="first last"]\n\n&nbsp;\n<h1 style="text-align: center;">Update V1.51 - 15th December 2013</h1>\n[hr] [list type="tick_bw"] [list_item]Fixed issue with missing icons after v1.5 update[/list_item] [list_item]Fixed other minor WordPress 3.8 styling issues[/list_item] <span style="line-height: 1.5em;">[/list]</span>\n\n&nbsp;\n\n[/fullwidth_text] [fullwidth_text alt_background="alt-seven" el_class="mt0 mb0 pb0 pmb0 bt0 bb0 no-arrow" width="1/1" el_position="first last"]\n\n&nbsp;\n<h1 style="text-align: center;">Update V1.5 - 13th December 2013</h1>\n[hr] [one_half] [list type="add"] [list_item]Added brand new image banner shortcodes, with intro animations[/list_item] [list_item]Added AJAX Search functionality to the header search[/list_item] [list_item]Added option of changing product image hover transition to fade or slide left[/list_item] [list_item]Updated Font Awesome to v4.0.3[/list_item] [list_item]Updated Revslider to v4.1[/list_item] [/list] [/one_half] [one_half_last] [list type="tick_bw"] [list_item]Fixed an issue where the meta on existing posts/pages would not save[/list_item] [list_item]Fixed other minor styling issues[/list_item] [list_item]Removed no script tag, not needed anymore[/list_item] [/list] [/one_half_last]\n\n&nbsp;\n\n[/fullwidth_text] [fullwidth_text alt_background="alt-seven" el_class="mt0 mb0 pb0 pmb0 bt0 bb0 no-arrow" width="1/1" el_position="first last"]\n\n&nbsp;\n<h1 style="text-align: center;">Update V1.4 - 28th November 2013</h1>\n[hr] [one_half] [list type="add"] [list_item]Added text within my orders when there are no orders placed[/list_item] [list_item]Improved the checkout process, now much slicker &amp; much better UX[/list_item] [list_item]Improved page builder media uploader to match latest version[/list_item] [list_item]Improved variation select box styling[/list_item] [list_item]Improved super search to not require widgets to be in the sidebar[/list_item] [list_item]Improved wishlist template to add in support for new options in YITH Wishlist[/list_item] [/list] [/one_half] [one_half_last] [list type="tick_bw"] [list_item]Fixed issue when woo commerce not active but super search enabled[/list_item] [list_item]Fixed shopping bag styling issue on mobile[/list_item] [list_item]Fixed result count issue[/list_item] [list_item]Fixed issue with search results page heading background[/list_item] [list_item]Fixed an issue with image zoom on product variations[/list_item] [list_item]Fixed issue with description on product pages[/list_item] [list_item]Fixed an issue with the checkout when register on checkout not enabled[/list_item] [list_item]Fixed one column footer[/list_item] [/list] [/one_half_last]\n\n&nbsp;\n\n[/fullwidth_text] [fullwidth_text alt_background="alt-seven" el_class="mt0 mb0 pb0 pmb0 bt0 bb0 no-arrow" width="1/1" el_position="first last"]\n\n&nbsp;\n<h1 style="text-align: center;">Update V1.3 - 9th August 2013</h1>\n[hr] [one_half] [list type="add"] [list_item]Added option to enable product zoom on product pages[/list_item] [list_item]Added new WooCommerce badge for free products[/list_item] [list_item]Added View Cart button to added to cart message on mobile devices[/list_item] [list_item]Added Pinterest share button to post pages[/list_item] [list_item]Improved mobile product listing styling[/list_item] [/list] [/one_half] [one_half_last] [list type="tick_bw"] [list_item]Fixed issues with standard WooCommerce shortcodes (requires WP 3.6)[/list_item] [list_item]Fixed minor styling issues[/list_item] [list_item]Fixed menu issue in Opera browser[/list_item] [/list] [/one_half_last]\n\n&nbsp;\n\n[/fullwidth_text] [fullwidth_text alt_background="alt-seven" el_class="mt0 mb0 pb0 pmb0 bt0 bb0 no-arrow" width="1/1" el_position="first last"]\n\n&nbsp;\n<h1 style="text-align: center;">Update V1.2 - 28th July 2013</h1>\n[hr] [one_half] [list type="add"] [list_item]Added catalog mode to WooCommerce[/list_item] [list_item]Added product category options to the product page builder assets[/list_item] [list_item]Added formatting to product description meta box[/list_item] [list_item]Added extra meta box for product short description[/list_item] [/list] [/one_half] [one_half_last] [list type="tick_bw"] [list_item]Fixed issue with menu drop downs on iPad[/list_item] [list_item]Fixed issue with revolution slider page builder asset[/list_item] [list_item]Fixed general minor WooCommerce issues[/list_item] [list_item]Fixed minor CSS issues[/list_item] [list_item]Fixed WooCommerce 1.6 issues[/list_item] [lis